<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَتَادَةَ ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">‌عِكْرِمَةَ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">‌ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ:</a> <span class="c2">«فَهَذِهِ وَهَذِهِ سَوَاءٌ، الْإِبْهَامُ وَالْخِنْصَرُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>